From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Ondrej Jirman <megi@xff.cz>
Date: Thu, 26 Sep 2024 23:00:02 +0200
Subject: input: cyttsp4: Add Cypress TMA445 touchscreen driver

This sensor is used on Pocketbook Touch Lux 3 (as part of XD4 toucscreen
enabled eInk panel). Add support for it.

This driver also implements self calibration, which is necessary to
perform after installing a new panel into the reader.

Signed-off-by: Ondrej Jirman <megi@xff.cz>
---
 drivers/input/touchscreen/Kconfig   |   13 +
 drivers/input/touchscreen/Makefile  |    1 +
 drivers/input/touchscreen/cyttsp4.c | 1053 ++++++++++
 3 files changed, 1067 insertions(+)

